{
  "openapi": "3.0.2",
  "paths": {
    "/api/v1": {
      "get": {
        "description": "Returns the API version and status. No authentication required.",
        "summary": "Health check",
        "tags": [
          "health"
        ],
        "parameters": [],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "200",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "version": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "v1"
                      ],
                      "description": "API version"
                    },
                    "status": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "ok"
                      ],
                      "description": "Service status"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "version",
                    "status"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/apps": {
      "get": {
        "description": "Returns all active installed apps for the authenticated group. Authenticate with JWT or API key.",
        "summary": "List installed apps",
        "tags": [
          "apps"
        ],
        "parameters": [],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "200",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                      "slug": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Unique app identifier"
                      },
                      "name": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "App display name"
                      },
                      "description": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "App description",
                        "nullable": true
                      },
                      "icon_url": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "App icon URL",
                        "nullable": true
                      },
                      "status": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "App status: active, inactive"
                      },
                      "visibility": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "App visibility: public, private"
                      }
                    },
                    "required": [
                      "slug",
                      "name",
                      "description",
                      "icon_url",
                      "status",
                      "visibility"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "401",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error code identifier"
                    },
                    "message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Human-readable error description"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "error",
                    "message"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "bearerAuth": []
          },
          {
            "apiKey": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/me": {
      "get": {
        "description": "Returns the authenticated user's profile information including display name, avatar, locale, role, and group membership.",
        "summary": "Get current user profile",
        "tags": [
          "me"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "authorization",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "200",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "id": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "User UUID"
                    },
                    "email": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "User email address"
                    },
                    "display_name": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Display name",
                      "nullable": true
                    },
                    "avatar_url": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Avatar URL",
                      "nullable": true
                    },
                    "locale": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Preferred locale code",
                      "nullable": true
                    },
                    "role": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "User role: admin or member"
                    },
                    "group_id": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Primary group UUID"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "id",
                    "email",
                    "display_name",
                    "avatar_url",
                    "locale",
                    "role",
                    "group_id"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "401",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error code, e.g. unauthorized"
                    },
                    "message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Details about the authentication failure"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "error",
                    "message"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "403": {
            "description": "403",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error code, e.g. forbidden"
                    },
                    "message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Details about why access was denied"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "error",
                    "message"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "bearerAuth": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/locales": {
      "get": {
        "description": "Returns the active locales configured for the group, with their display names and default flag.",
        "summary": "List active locales",
        "tags": [
          "locales"
        ],
        "parameters": [],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "200",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                      "code": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Locale code (e.g. en, es, ca)"
                      },
                      "name": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Locale display name"
                      },
                      "is_default": {
                        "type": "boolean",
                        "description": "Whether this is the default locale"
                      }
                    },
                    "required": [
                      "code",
                      "name",
                      "is_default"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/admin/apps/todo": {
      "get": {
        "description": "Returns all todo items across all groups. Requires admin role.",
        "summary": "List all todo items (admin)",
        "tags": [
          "admin",
          "apps",
          "todo",
          "Admin"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "authorization",
            "in": "header",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "200",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                      "id": {
                        "type": "number",
                        "description": "Todo item ID"
                      },
                      "title": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Todo title"
                      },
                      "completed": {
                        "type": "boolean",
                        "description": "Whether the todo is completed"
                      },
                      "created_at": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "ISO 8601 creation timestamp"
                      },
                      "user_id": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Owner user UUID"
                      },
                      "group_id": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Group UUID"
                      },
                      "visibility": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Visibility: public, private"
                      }
                    },
                    "required": [
                      "id",
                      "title",
                      "completed",
                      "created_at",
                      "user_id",
                      "group_id",
                      "visibility"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "401",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error code, e.g. unauthorized"
                    },
                    "message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Details about the authentication failure"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "error",
                    "message"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "403": {
            "description": "403",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error code, e.g. forbidden"
                    },
                    "message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Details about why access was denied"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "error",
                    "message"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "500",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error code identifier"
                    },
                    "message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Human-readable error description"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "error",
                    "message"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "bearerAuth": []
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "info": {
    "title": "027Apps API",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "# 027Apps API\n\nAPI pública de la plataforma 027Apps — espacio compartido para aplicaciones, tareas y herramientas entre grupos.\n\n## Autenticación\n\nLa API soporta dos métodos de autenticación:\n\n- **JWT Bearer Token** (recomendado): obtenido al iniciar sesión. Enviar como `Authorization: Bearer <token>`.\n- **API Key**: para acceso de servidor a servidor. Enviar como `X-API-Key: <key>`.\n\n## Estados de respuesta\n\n| Código | Significado |\n|--------|-------------|\n| 200 | Success |\n| 201 | Created |\n| 400 | Bad Request |\n| 401 | Unauthorized |\n| 403 | Forbidden |\n| 404 | Not Found |\n| 422 | Validation Error |\n| 500 | Internal Server Error |\n\n## Notas\n\n- Todos los endpoints que requieren autenticación devuelven `401` si falta el token.\n- Los endpoints de administración requieren rol `admin`.\n- Los endpoints de apps dinámicas (proxy) no están documentados aquí por ser específicos de cada app instalada."
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://localhost:3000",
      "description": "Local development"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://027app-eric-rf.vercel.app",
      "description": "Production"
    }
  ],
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "bearerAuth": {
        "type": "http",
        "scheme": "bearer",
        "bearerFormat": "JWT",
        "description": "JWT token obtenido al iniciar sesión en la aplicación"
      },
      "apiKey": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "in": "header",
        "name": "X-API-Key",
        "description": "API Key generada desde el panel de administración"
      }
    }
  }
}